(19, 'Coffee Slimmer Pro', 'doorbin1122@gmail.com', 'Coffee Slimmer Pro is marketed as a dietary supplement designed to help individuals lose weight by the natural benefits of coffee. Combining the stimulating effects of caffeine with other natural ingredients, this supplement aims to promote fat-burning, boost metabolism, and curb appetite, all of which are essential components for effective weight management. \r\nCoffee Slimmer Pro may assist in weight loss by supporting fat burning and energy levels, it\'s important to remember that no supplement is a magic solution.  Furthermore, individual results can vary, and it\'s always a good idea to consult with a healthcare professional before starting any new supplement, especially for those with underlying health conditions or concerns. \r\nCoffee Slimmer Pro could be helpful for those looking to lose weight, but it should be viewed as a part of a broader lifestyle change that includes healthy eating and regular physical activity buy coffee here https://coffeeslimmerpro.com/special/#aff=Tullah1', 'sent', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-12-24 08:11:43', '2024-12-24 08:11:43', '83272379796'),
