 you are worried you stick to the roads rather than walk through the parks.  The roads are well-lit and generally there are a lot of people about at night.\"},{\"title\":\"Can I come on my own?\",\"content\":\"YES!  Many of our customers come alone to events, it\\u2019s never a problem and you will be welcomed warmly.\"}]', '[{\"code\":\"ticket_vip\",\"name\":\"Ticket Vip\",\"price\":\"1000\",\"number\":\"10\"},{\"code\":\"ticket_group_tickets\",\"name\":\"Group Tickets\",\"price\":\"500\",\"number\":\"10\"}]', 1, '15:00', 2100.00, 533.00, NULL, 1, '[{\"name\":\"Event service\",\"price\":\"100\",\"type\":\"one_time\"}]', 4.4, NULL, 'publish', 1, 6, 6, NULL, '2024-12-10 05:11:34', '2024-12-12 12:06:15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hour', 6),
