(15, 'Cannes and Antibes Night Tour', 'cannes-and-antibes-night-tour', '<p>Start and end in San Francisco! With the in-depth cultural tour Northern California Summer 2019, you have a 8 day tour package taking you through San Francisco, USA and 9 other destinations in USA. Northern California Summer 2019 includes accommodation as well as an expert guide, meals, transport and more.</p>\r\n<h4>HIGHLIGHTS</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Visit the Museum of Modern Art in Manhattan</li>\r\n<li>See amazing works of contemporary art, including Vincent van Gogh\'s The Starry Night</li>\r\n<li>Check out Campbell\'s Soup Cans by Warhol and The Dance (I) by Matisse</li>\r\n<li>Behold masterpieces by Gauguin, Dali, Picasso, and Pollock</li>\r\n<li>Enjoy free audio guides available in English, French, German, Italian, Spanish, Portuguese</li>\r\n</ul>', 335, 58, 'From the iconic to the unexpected, the city of San Francisco never ceases to surprise. Kick-start your effortlessly delivered Northern California holiday in the cosmopolitan hills of \'The City\'. Join your Travel Director and fellow travellers for a Welcome Reception at your hotel.Welcome Reception', 1, 1, 'UCSF Helen Diller Family', '36.201066', '-88.112292', 12, NULL, '37,38,39,40,41,42,43', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfEiKK-iX70', 2100.00, 1008.00, 6, 4, 1, 19, '[{\"title\":\"When and where does the tour end?\",\"content\":\"Your tour will conclude in San Francisco on Day 8 of the trip. There are no activities planned for this day so you\'re free to depart at any time. We highly recommend booking post-accommodation to give yourself time to fully experience the wonders of this iconic city!\"},{\"title\":\"When and where does the tour start?\",\"content\":\"Day 1 of this tour is an arrivals day, which gives you a chance to settle into your hotel and explore Los Angeles. The only planned activity for this day is an evening welcome meeting at 7pm, where you can get to know your guides and fellow travellers. Please be aware that the meeting point is subject to change until your final documents are released.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you arrange airport transfers?\",\"content\":\"Airport transfers are not included in the price of this tour, however you can book for an arrival transfer in advance. In this case a tour operator representative will be at the airport to greet you. To arrange this please contact our customer service team once you have a confirmed booking.\"},{\"title\":\"What is the age range\",\"content\":\"This tour has an age range of 12-70 years old, this means children under the age of 12 will not be eligible to participate in this tour. However, if you are over 70 years please contact us as you may be eligible to join the tour if you fill out G Adventures self-assessment form.\"}]', 'publish', NULL, 6, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-12-10 05:11:14', '2025-01-06 08:53:56', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"Specialized bilingual guide\"},{\"title\":\"Private Transport\"},{\"title\":\"Entrance fees (Cable and car and Moon Valley)\"},{\"title\":\"Box lunch water, banana apple and chocolate\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Additional Services\"},{\"title\":\"Insurance\"},{\"title\":\"Drink\"},{\"title\":\"Tickets\"}]', '[{\"image_id\":\"107\",\"title\":\"Day 1\",\"desc\":\"Los Angeles\",\"content\":\"There are no activities planned until an evening welcome meeting. Additional Notes: We highly recommend booking pre-tour accommodation to fully experience this crazy city.\"},{\"image_id\":\"109\",\"title\":\"Day 2\",\"desc\":\"Lake Havasu City\",\"content\":\"Pack up the van in the morning and check out the stars on the most famous sidewalk in Hollywood on an orientation tour\"},{\"image_id\":\"108\",\"title\":\"Day 3\",\"desc\":\"Las Vegas\\/Bakersfield\",\"content\":\"Travel to one of the country\'s most rugged landscapes \\u2014 the legendary Death Valley, California. Soak in the dramatic landscape. In the afternoon, continue on to Bakersfield for the night.\"},{\"image_id\":\"107\",\"title\":\"Day 4\",\"desc\":\"San Francisco\",\"content\":\"We highly recommend booking post-accommodation to fully experience this famous city.\"}]', 4.0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jan 18’ - Dec 21’', '12+', 'Airpot', 1, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(16, 'Europe Tour 6 nights 7 days', 'river-cruise-tour-on-the-seine', '<p>Start and end in Brussels! With the in-depth cultural tour Europe Tour 2025, you have a 7 day tour package taking you through Brussels, Brussels and 2 other destinations in Europe. Europe Tour 2025&nbsp;includes accommodation as well as an expert guide, meals, transport and more.</p>\r\n<h4>HIGHLIGHTS</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Belgium <strong>(2 nights)</strong></span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-US\">Luxembourg</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-US\">France <strong>(2 nights)</strong></span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-US\">Switzerland <strong>(2 Nights)</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 336, 59, 'From the iconic to the unexpected, the city of San Francisco never ceases to surprise. Kick-start your effortlessly delivered Northern California holiday in the cosmopolitan hills of \'The City\'. Join your Travel Director and fellow travellers for a Welcome Reception at your hotel.Welcome Reception', 1, 12, 'Nevada, US', '36.401066', '-88.312292', 12, NULL, '37,38,39,40,41,42,43', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UfEiKK-iX70', 390000.00, 390000.00, 6, 7, 1, 10, '[{\"title\":\"When and where does the tour end?\",\"content\":\"Your tour will conclude in San Francisco on Day 8 of the trip. There are no activities planned for this day so you\'re free to depart at any time. We highly recommend booking post-accommodation to give yourself time to fully experience the wonders of this iconic city!\"},{\"title\":\"When and where does the tour start?\",\"content\":\"Day 1 of this tour is an arrivals day, which gives you a chance to settle into your hotel and explore Los Angeles. The only planned activity for this day is an evening welcome meeting at 7pm, where you can get to know your guides and fellow travellers. Please be aware that the meeting point is subject to change until your final documents are released.\"},{\"title\":\"Do you arrange airport transfers?\",\"content\":\"Airport transfers are not included in the price of this tour, however you can book for an arrival transfer in advance. In this case a tour operator representative will be at the airport to greet you. To arrange this please contact our customer service team once you have a confirmed booking.\"},{\"title\":\"What is the age range\",\"content\":\"This tour has an age range of 12-70 years old, this means children under the age of 12 will not be eligible to participate in this tour. However, if you are over 70 years please contact us as you may be eligible to join the tour if you fill out G Adventures self-assessment form.\"}]', 'publish', NULL, 6, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-12-10 05:11:14', '2025-01-23 10:06:29', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"Return Air ticket\"},{\"title\":\"Airport pick up and drop off\"},{\"title\":\"Accommodation (3 * Hotel) Twin sharing basis with complimentary breakfast\"},{\"title\":\"All train tickets\"},{\"title\":\"Sight-seeing (As per itenary)\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Visas (Visa fee) & Travel Insurance\"},{\"title\":\"All optional activities and tickets not included in the itinerary\"},{\"title\":\"Meals not included like Lunch and Dinner\"},{\"title\":\"Personal expenses (laundry, internet, phone calls etc.\"},{\"title\":\"Meals (including tips) and drinks not included in the itinerary\"},{\"title\":\"City entrance fees + taxes\"},{\"title\":\"Any Alcohol & beverage\"},{\"title\":\"Personal Cost\"},{\"title\":\"Personal Tips\"}]', '[{\"image_id\":\"107\",\"title\":\"Day 1\",\"desc\":\"Arrival \\u2013 Brussels\",\"content\":\"Arrival in Belgium and transfer to the hotel. After check in evening time explore the city and take dinner. Overnight in Brussels. At first visit forward to visit Grand Palace (take taxi) then Manekeen pis and European quarter.\"},{\"image_id\":\"109\",\"title\":\"Day 2\",\"desc\":\"Brussels\",\"content\":\"After breakfast move forward to whole day tour., whole day tour and its main sights, such as (Luxembarg and Donat) around 11-hour visit.  Overnight in Brussels.\"},{\"image_id\":\"108\",\"title\":\"Day 3\",\"desc\":\"Brussels - Paris (France)\",\"content\":\"Breakfast at the hotel. In the morning departure from hotel and move forward to France. Arrival in Paris and time for check-in at hotel. After check in evening time explore Paris city and take dinner. Overnight in Paris. (From Brussels to Paris train time morning around 10:10 am and it takes around 1 and half hour journey to reach Paris - France reach around 11:40 am), Evening time visit Eiffel tower and surroundings area. And doing River Cruise.\"},{\"image_id\":\"107\",\"title\":\"Day 4\",\"desc\":\"Paris\",\"content\":\"Breakfast at the hotel. Whole day tour \\u2013 Louvre Museum, Arc De triomphe roof top and so on.\"},{\"image_id\":null,\"title\":\"Day 5\",\"desc\":\"Paris \\u2013 Zurich (Switzerland)\",\"content\":\"Breakfast at the hotel. In the morning departure from hotel and move forward Switzerland. Arrival in Zurich and time for check-in at hotel. After check in evening time explore Zurich city Overnight in Zurich. (From Paris to Zurich train time morning around 9:10 am and it takes around 4-hour journey to reach Zurich \\u2013 Switzerland reach around 2:30 pm) around 490 KM distance.\"},{\"image_id\":null,\"title\":\"Day 6\",\"desc\":\"Zurich\",\"content\":\"Explore Zurikh city (Whole day tour). Overnight in Zurikh.\"},{\"image_id\":null,\"title\":\"Day 7\",\"desc\":\"Departure Zurich - Dhaka\",\"content\":\"After breakfast Check out from hotel. Move forward to Zurich airport for return back to Dhaka.\"}]', 5.0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, 'Jan 18’ - Dec 21’', '12+', 'Airpot', 1, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(17, 'Voluptatem anim sun', 'voluptatem-anim-sun', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, NULL, NULL, 'Occaecat cupidatat u', NULL, NULL, 78, 3, 0, 0, NULL, 'publish', NULL, 6, 6, '2025-01-06 08:19:51', NULL, NULL, '2025-01-06 08:19:28', '2025-01-06 08:19:51', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '03-Aug-1987', 'Aut quas nobis omnis', 'Ad cum fuga Exercit', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 18),
